{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-markdown-remark-js","path":"/community/community/social-media-guide.md","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Operate First"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"7a482a98-870c-5e16-aeb6-a0650450c068","html":"<h1 id=\"social-media-guide\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#social-media-guide\" aria-label=\"social media guide permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Social media guide</h1>\n<p>We aim to create content that encourages interaction, participation, and conversation.\nWhen posting to social media under Operate First, be sure to:</p>\n<ul class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li>Ensure content is accurate</li>\n<li>Proofread the post carefully</li>\n<li>Provide links to related pages or resources</li>\n<li>Verify that your links work</li>\n<li>Request review on the content and gain approval before posting</li>\n<li>Adhere to the Red Hat <a href=\"https://source.redhat.com/groups/public/social-media-at-red-hat/social_guidelines_nav\">Social Media Guidelines</a> and <a href=\"https://source.redhat.com/groups/public/social-media-at-red-hat/social_guidelines_nav/social_media_style_guide\">Style Guide</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"general-goals\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#general-goals\" aria-label=\"general goals permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>General goals</h2>\n<ol class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li>Raise awareness on the Operate First initiative</li>\n<li>Grow the community of users and contributors</li>\n<li>Increase interaction and dialogue within the community</li>\n<li>Drive traffic to the website</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"metrics\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#metrics\" aria-label=\"metrics permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Metrics</h3>\n<p>A variety of metrics can be used to measure the effectiveness of social media efforts for Operate First.</p>\n<h4 id=\"universal\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#universal\" aria-label=\"universal permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Universal</h4>\n<ul class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li>Website traffic from social media</li>\n<li>Likes</li>\n<li>Comments</li>\n<li>Posting cadence</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"twitter\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#twitter\" aria-label=\"twitter permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Twitter</h4>\n<ul class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li>Followers</li>\n<li>Mentions</li>\n<li>Retweets</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"youtube\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#youtube\" aria-label=\"youtube permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Youtube</h4>\n<ul class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li>Subscribers</li>\n<li>Views</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"twitter-guidance\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#twitter-guidance\" aria-label=\"twitter guidance permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Twitter guidance</h2>\n<p>Tweets for <a href=\"https://twitter.com/OperateFirst\">Operate First</a> are written collaboratively and posted via the merging of pull requests to the twitter repository.\nVisit <a href=\"https://github.com/operate-first/operate-first-twitter/blob/main/tweets/README.md\">this page</a> for instructions on writing and posting tweets.</p>\n<p>Ideally, a tweet should be posted for each Operate First Youtube video promoting that content.\nTwitter can also be used to promote Operate First in general and provide updates on the initiative to the community.</p>\n<p>When writing copy for a tweet, tag people and software accounts directly for better reach.\nFor example, use @trinodb in your tweet rather than Trino.</p>\n<p>Donâ€™t overuse hashtags. One or two is sufficient, more may trigger algorithms to work against your tweet being highlighted.</p>\n<h2 id=\"youtube-guidance\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#youtube-guidance\" aria-label=\"youtube guidance permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Youtube guidance</h2>\n<h3 id=\"title\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#title\" aria-label=\"title permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Title</h3>\n<p>The title should capture the overall subject of the video using as few words as possible.\nThink descriptive, simple, and brief.\nPreviously, video titles have not capitalized in a consistent way and switch between sentence case and title case.\nMoving forward, use the title case for all Youtube videos in order to establish consistency.</p>\n<h3 id=\"description\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#description\" aria-label=\"description permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Description</h3>\n<p>The description should provide an initial summary that describes the content of the video itself; this summary should be clear and concise.\nNext, share links or resources of any kind that are related and relevant to the video.\nAdditionally, provide a way of contacting the creator(s) or other Operate First experts to ask questions or start a dialogue.</p>\n<h4 id=\"description-template\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#description-template\" aria-label=\"description template permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Description template</h4>\n<blockquote>\n<p>In this video, we will â€¦</p>\n<p>Related links:</p>\n<ul class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li>Any specific repos, pages, guides or tutorials, etc</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.operate-first.cloud/\">Operate First Website</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/operate-first\">Operate First GitHub organization</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Questions? Contact us in <a href=\"https://join.slack.com/t/operatefirst/shared_invite/zt-o2gn4wn8-O39g7sthTAuPCvaCNRnLww\">slack</a> or leave a comment on this video!</p>\n<p>Subscribe down below, and check us out on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/OperateFirst\">Twitter</a> to keep up with all things Operate First.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"audience\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#audience\" aria-label=\"audience permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Audience</h3>\n<p>Since children are not the primary audience for Operate First videos, mark videos not made for kids.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0fe941dd135b48fe218c5dadf4a97984/87254/audience.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.05405405405405%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Audience specification\"\n        title=\"Audience specification\"\n        src=\"/static/0fe941dd135b48fe218c5dadf4a97984/fcda8/audience.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0fe941dd135b48fe218c5dadf4a97984/12f09/audience.png 148w,\n/static/0fe941dd135b48fe218c5dadf4a97984/e4a3f/audience.png 295w,\n/static/0fe941dd135b48fe218c5dadf4a97984/fcda8/audience.png 590w,\n/static/0fe941dd135b48fe218c5dadf4a97984/87254/audience.png 604w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","fields":{"srcLink":"https://github.com/operate-first/community/blob/master/social-media-guide.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"","description":null,"extraClasses":null,"banner":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"7a482a98-870c-5e16-aeb6-a0650450c068"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1764348645","2823140819","3000541721","3606484676"]}